data.text: Actually, I think I'm quite good with children. I love kids, maybe it's because I'm a kid as well here. And I like to play with kids. I think it's really hilarious. They definitely make it exhausted and tired  but I do enjoy playing with kids. And actually sometimes in the local orphanage, when it's Christmas time, we dresses Santa Claus and elves and sometimes we play with little kids and it's quite nice. I love kids. They're so nice. I mean they're just full of life and smiles. But they bite sometimes. They bite you and they get at your back and everything.
